<p>
The author of this paper is Kelly Haydon, UCAVH Project Manager (<a
href="mailto:kelly.haydon@tv.cuny.edu">kelly.haydon@tv.cuny.edu</a>). The
project was spearheaded by CUNY-TV staff members David Rice, Director of
Archives, and Catriona Schlosser, Archivist, both of whom can be reached at <a
href="mailto:archive@tv.cuny.edu">archive@tv.cuny.edu</a>. The contact at Bronx
